---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main class="page-main" data-pagefind-ignore>
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">研究</h1>
    </section>

    <section style="display: grid; gap: 1.25rem;">

      <div class="card">
        <h2>研究兴趣</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
          <div>
            <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.35rem; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.05em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6366f1;">质谱与仪器分析</h3>
            <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.93rem;">Orbitrap 高分辨质谱；碰撞诱导解离碎裂机理；撞击型 TOF-MS 实验与数据分析；SELINA 撞击电离平台设计与组装；生物分子碎片图谱鉴定；面向海洋世界的生物标志物预测与检测。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.35rem; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.05em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6366f1;">微流控与器件制造</h3>
            <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.93rem;">微流控芯片设计与加工；DLP、FDM 等 3D 打印技术；化学发光微流控体系的构建。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.35rem; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.05em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6366f1;">数据分析与计算化学</h3>
            <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.93rem;">基于 Python 的 MS/MS 数据自动化处理与可视化；基于 ORCA 的量子化学计算；键解离能与分子碎裂分析。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.35rem; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.05em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6366f1;">材料与光化学</h3>
            <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.93rem;">高分子化学；光固化与光聚合体系；化学发光诱导光聚合；双光子光刻；化学镀金属图案化。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>当前工作</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
          博士阶段在莱比锡大学 Prof. Bernd Abel 课题组，主要开展以下方向的研究：
        </p>
        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; display:grid; gap:0.4rem; font-size:0.93rem;">
          <li>高分辨率 Orbitrap 质谱撞击诱导碎裂与碎片图谱分析</li>
          <li>撞击型飞行时间质谱（TOF-MS）实验</li>
          <li>土卫二（卡西尼-惠更斯号）相关生命信号分析</li>
          <li>撞击粒子实验平台 SELINA 的设计与组装</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>发表论文</h2>

        <div style="display:grid; gap:0.85rem;">
          <div style="padding: 1rem 1.15rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12); border-radius: 0.75rem;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.3rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.93rem; line-height:1.5;">
              <a href="https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acsmacrolett.0c00003" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:inherit; text-decoration:none;">Chemiluminescence Induced Cationic Photopolymerization Using Sulfonium Salt ↗</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.84rem; line-height:1.6;">
              <strong style="color:#374151;">Wang C.</strong>, Meng X., Li Z., Li M., Jin M., Liu R., Yagci Y.
              <br /><em>ACS Macro Letters</em>, 2020, 9(4), 471–475.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div style="padding: 1rem 1.15rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12); border-radius: 0.75rem;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.3rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.93rem; line-height:1.5;">
              <a href="https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/photopolymer/33/3/33_285/_article" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:inherit; text-decoration:none;">Thiol-ene-acrylate Ternary Photosensitive Resins for DLP 3D Printing ↗</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.84rem; line-height:1.6;">
              Wang C., <strong style="color:#374151;">Wang C.</strong>, Li Z.
              <br /><em>Journal of Photopolymer Science and Technology</em>, 2020, 33(3), 285–290.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div style="padding: 1rem 1.15rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12); border-radius: 0.75rem;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.3rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.93rem; line-height:1.5;">
              <a href="https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2019/py/c9py01262a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:inherit; text-decoration:none;">Near-infrared Light induced Cationic Polymerization based on Upconversion and Ferrocenium Photochemistry ↗</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.84rem; line-height:1.6;">
              Meng X., Lu H., Li Z., <strong style="color:#374151;">Wang C.</strong>, Liu R., Guan X., Yagci Y.
              <br /><em>Polymer Chemistry</em>, 2019, 10(41), 5574–5577.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>数据库</h2>
        <div style="display:grid; gap:0.85rem;">
          <div style="padding: 1rem 1.15rem; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12); border-radius: 0.75rem;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.3rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.93rem; line-height:1.5;">
              Energy-dependence MS/MS of amino acids and peptides — raw positive and negative
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 0.6rem; color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.84rem;">
              Wang C. et al. · Zenodo
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://zenodo.org/records/18270480"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              style="font-size:0.84rem; color:#6366f1; font-weight:500; text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:3px;"
            >zenodo.org/records/18270480 ↗</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>方法与工具</h2>
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap:0.5rem 1.5rem;">
          {[
            'Orbitrap 高分辨质谱',
            '撞击型 TOF-MS',
            'Python MS/MS 数据处理',
            'ORCA 量子化学计算',
            'DLP / FDM 3D 打印',
            '微流控芯片制造',
            '科研绘图与统计分析',
            '光聚合体系与光化学',
          ].map(item => (
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem; font-size:0.88rem; color:#374151; padding:0.4rem 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
              <span style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#6366f1;flex-shrink:0;"></span>
              {item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
